    <title>The &#039;Great Full Debt Tour&#039;: Field Reports from the Tea Party Debt Commission</title>
    <link>http://www.freedomworks.org/blog/dean-clancy/the-great-full-debt-tour-2011-field-reports-with-p</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Tea Party Debt commission road tour is in full swing. We&#039;ve taken to calling it the &quot;Great Full Debt Tour.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1st Field hearing (Salt Lake City, Utah):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The first field hearing of the TPDC took place in Salt Lake City, Utah, on Thursday, September 1, 2011. Hundreds of local activists and interested citizens packed into the standing-room-only meeting at Noah&#039;s Conference Center in South Jordan, Utah.&amp;nbsp;Attendees also included a large number of local elected officials and aspiring candidates for office.&amp;nbsp;Participants lined up to offer numerous ideas for specific cuts and reforms. After introductions by local activist Dan McCay and FreedomWorks President and CEO Matt Kibbe, the audience heard a presentation on the budget crisis by Dean Clancy of FreedomWorks, who presented initial findings from the group&#039;s online budget poll (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.teapartydebtcommission.com/&quot; title=&quot;www.TeaPartyDebtCommission.com&quot;&gt;www.TeaPartyDebtCommission.com&lt;/a&gt;), which allows voters to prioritize spending cuts. Members of the Utah Advisory Committee of the Tea Party Debt Commission sat at the dais, listening to budget-cutting suggestions:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Kim Coleman - Salt Lake 9-12, Utah Rising&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;David Kirham - Utah Rising (Mr. Kirkham is also a national TPDC commissioner)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;D.J. Schanz – Austrian Economics Club of Utah, Campaign For Liberty&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Peter Cannon – Davis County 9-12&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dan McCay – Utah FreedomWorks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Jacqueline Smith – The S.T.A.R. Forum&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Austin Linford – Republican Party&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Kim Weis – Box Elder 9-12&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Michael Stoddard – Austrian Economics Club of Utah&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mia Love - Mayor, Saratoga Springs, Utah&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2nd field hearing (Orlando, Florida):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The 2nd field hearing of the TPDC took place on Friday, September 23, 2011, during the Florida CPAC convention in Orlando, FL. At the Denny&#039;s restaurant across from the Orange County Convention Center,&amp;nbsp;Rev. C. L. Bryant led the opening prayer, and then&amp;nbsp;FreedomWorks President Matt Kibbe addressed the crowd on the importance of influencing Washington&#039;s budget and debt debates from the grassroots up. FreedomWorks legislative counsel and health care VP Dean Clancy walked the group through a presentation (see photos below). Former House Majority Leader Dick Armey discussed the TPDC in the context of the 2012 elections. The Commission heard many constructive ideas from the audience. For example, one audience member made a compelling case for devolving federal highway funding and responsibilities to the states. Another explained the massive challenges that Medicaid poses for Florida residents and taxpayers.&amp;nbsp;Several members of the Florida Advisory Committee to the Tea Party Debt Commission were present, including:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sharon Calvert - Tampa Tea Party&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Karen Jaroch - Tampa 9/12&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tim Curtis&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Karin Hoffman - DCworksforUS, South Florida&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/TPDC_field_hearing_Dennys_Orlando_2011-09-23_Dick_Armey.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Dick Armey at 2011-09-23 TPDC field hearing&quot; title=&quot;Dick Armey at 2011-09-23 TPDC field hearing&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/TPDC_field_hearing_Dennys_Orlando_2011-09-23_Matt_Kibbe.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Matt Kibbe at TPDC hearing Dennys Orlando 2011-09-23&quot; title=&quot;Matt Kibbe at TPDC hearing Dennys Orlando 2011-09-23&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission/&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/TPDC_hearing_Dennys_Orlando_2011-09-23.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;TPDC hearing Dennys Orlando 2011-09-23&quot; title=&quot;TPDC hearing Dennys Orlando 2011-09-23&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3rd field hearing (Ogden, Utah):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Commission&#039;s third hearing took place on Monday, September 26, 2011, in the Black Box Theater auditorium of the Weber County Public Library, Pleasant Valley Branch, in Ogden, Utah. Rep. Rob Bishop (R-UT) spoke at the event and listened to audience comments, as did state Sen. Dan Liljenquist and other local elected officials.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/IMAG0556.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;TPDC Ogden 2011-09-26 (1)&quot; title=&quot;TPDC Ogden 2011-09-26 (1)&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;359&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/IMAG0563.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;TPDC Ogden 2011-09-26 (4)&quot; title=&quot;TPDC Ogden 2011-09-26 (4)&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/IMAG0562.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;TPDC Ogden 2011-09-26 (2)&quot; title=&quot;TPDC Ogden 2011-09-26 (2)&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For more information, visit the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission&quot;&gt;Tea Party Debt Commission main page.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;og_rss_groups&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
