    <title>Update on the Fight for Issues 2 &amp; 3 in Ohio</title>
    <link>http://www.freedomworks.org/blog/jeboch/update-on-the-fight-for-issues-2-3-in-ohio</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Thanks to the huge response of Ohioans to an email sent out last week, thousands of yard signs and door hangers produced by FreedomWorks began arriving at distribution points around the state today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please take a moment to visit our website &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.yesforjobs.com&quot;&gt;www.yesforjobs.com&lt;/a&gt; and sign the pledge there indicating support for Issues 2 &amp;amp; 3.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Next month, FreedomWorks will host an official field hearing of the Tea Party Debt Commission in Cincinnatti where yard signs and door hangers will be available for pick up. For more information or to RSVP visit: &lt;a href=&quot;http://connect.freedomworks.org/node/177745&quot;&gt;http://connect.freedomworks.org/node/177745&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Meanwhile, FreedomWorks has created door hangers that can be downloaded and printed at home. Go &lt;a href=&quot;http://blogs.freedomworks.org/files/FWOhioDoorHanger.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;HERE&lt;/a&gt; to download and print your own.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#039;re also looking forward to participating in other events around the state between now and November. If you would like to help organize or host an event in your city, please let us know by emailing &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:dspielman@freedomworks.org&quot;&gt;dspielman@freedomworks.org&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&#039;s important to remember that this fight isn&#039;t just about Issues 2 &amp;amp; 3. It&#039;s about sending a message to public servants everywhere that government exists to serve the people, not the other way around.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With your help, this November we&#039;ll return Ohio to the taxpayers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;og_rss_groups&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
