  <item>
    <title>Tea Party Debt Commission Hits a &quot;Grand Slam&quot; in Orlando</title>
    <link>http://www.freedomworks.org/blog/dean-clancy/tea-party-debt-commission-wows-orlando-0</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Tea Party Debt Commission took Orlando by storm at a local Denny&#039;s restaurant Friday near the Orange County Convention Center. Participants agreed both the food and the testimony were &quot;grand slam.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/original/TPDC_logo_1.png&quot; alt=&quot;Tea Party Debt Commission&quot; title=&quot;Tea Party Debt Commission&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-original&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Just steps from the big Florida Conservative Political Action Conference (CPAC) that drew tea party types and GOP presidential hopefuls from all across the country, the lunch hour hearing was a big success.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The audience included interested citizens, journalists, local tea party activists, all packed in a Denny&#039;s back room to discuss budgets, baselines, and the national debt.&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Rev. C. L. Bryant led the opening prayer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Then&amp;nbsp;FreedomWorks President Matt Kibbe addressed the crowd on the importance of influencing Washington&#039;s budget and debt debates from the grassroots up.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;FreedomWorks legislative counsel and health care VP Dean Clancy walked the group through a brief budget and debt background &lt;a href=&quot;http://blogs.freedomworks.org/files/TPDC_FieldHearing092311OrlandoFL.pdf&quot;&gt;presentation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Former House Majority Leader Dick Armey discussed the TPDC in the context of the 2012 elections.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Several members of the Florida Advisory Committee to the Tea Party Debt Commission were present, including:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sharon Calvert - Tampa Tea Party&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Karen Jaroch - Tampa 9/12&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tim Curtis&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Karin Hoffman - DCworksforUS, South Florida&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Most of the meeting was spent in hearing numerous constructive ideas from the audience. For example, one audience member made a compelling case for devolving federal highway funding and responsibilities to the states. Another explained the massive challenges that Medicaid poses for Florida residents and taxpayers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/TPDC_field_hearing_Dennys_Orlando_2011-09-23_Dick_Armey.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Dick Armey at 2011-09-23 TPDC field hearing&quot; title=&quot;Dick Armey at 2011-09-23 TPDC field hearing&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/TPDC_field_hearing_Dennys_Orlando_2011-09-23_Matt_Kibbe.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Matt Kibbe at TPDC hearing Dennys Orlando 2011-09-23&quot; title=&quot;Matt Kibbe at TPDC hearing Dennys Orlando 2011-09-23&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission/&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.freedomworks.org/files/imagecache/full/TPDC_hearing_Dennys_Orlando_2011-09-23.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;TPDC hearing Dennys Orlando 2011-09-23&quot; title=&quot;TPDC hearing Dennys Orlando 2011-09-23&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-full&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;To learn more about the Commission, or to find a list of upcoming field hearings, please visit our &lt;a href=&quot;http://www/freedomworks.org/teapartydebtcommission&quot;&gt;Tea Party Debt Commission&lt;/a&gt; page.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;To RSVP to attend a hearing, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://connect.freedomworks.org/node/178280&quot;&gt;FreedomConnector&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and search for the specific event by location and the key words &quot;tea party debt commission.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;og_rss_groups&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
